Package: madcounter
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: text analysis utility for character, word, and line statistics
 madcounter reads a text file and generates detailed statistics about
 its content. It can analyze individual characters, whitespace-separated
 words, and newline-separated lines.
 .
 Features:
  - Character frequency analysis with ASCII values and positions
  - Word frequency analysis sorted alphabetically
  - Line frequency analysis with position tracking
  - Longest word(s) and longest line(s) detection
  - Batch mode for processing multiple files
  - Optional output file support
